sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User
    participant React as React SPA
    participant AS as Authorization Server
    participant DB as auth.users (PostgreSQL)
    participant US as User Service

    User->>React: Click "Sign in"
    React->>AS: GET /oauth2/authorize<br/>(client_id, redirect_uri, code_challenge)
    AS->>User: Login page (form login)
    User->>AS: POST /login (email + password)
    AS->>DB: loadUserByUsername(email)
    DB-->>AS: UserDetails (passwordHash, roles)
    AS->>AS: BCrypt.verify(password, passwordHash)
    AS-->>React: redirect → /callback?code=xyz
    React->>AS: POST /oauth2/token<br/>(code, code_verifier)
    AS->>AS: OAuth2TokenCustomizer triggered
    AS->>US: GET /users/{sub}/profile<br/>(internal M2M token)
    US-->>AS: user_id, display_name
    AS->>AS: Adds roles, user_id, display_name to JWT
    AS->>AS: Signs JWT with RSA private key<br/>(from auth.signing_keys)
    AS-->>React: Access Token + ID Token + Refresh Token
    React->>React: Reads ID Token<br/>(display_name for UI)
    React->>US: GET /me<br/>Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
    US->>US: Validates JWT with public key<br/>via GET /oauth2/jwks
    US-->>React: User profile data